<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css">
    <link rel="icon" type="image" sizes="96x96" href="/images/favicon.png">
    <title>Locadora de filmes</title>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-dark">
      <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
        <img src="/images/logo.png" width="50" height="auto" alt="">
      </a>
    </header>
    
    <div class="mt-3 ml-5 mr-5">
    <h1 >Bem Vindo à <img src="/images/logo.png" width="100" height="100" alt=""/>LOCADORAFA!</h1>
      <h2>Seu sistema de Aluguel de filmes sem sair de casa!</h2>

      <div class="container mb-5 mt-5">
        <div class="pricing card-deck flex-column flex-md-row mb-3">
            <div class="card card-pricing text-center px-3 mb-4">
                <span class="h6 w-60 mx-auto px-4 py-1 rounded-bottom bg-primary text-white shadow-sm">Iniciante</span>
                <div class="bg-transparent card-header pt-4 border-0">
                    <h1 class="h1 font-weight-normal text-primary text-center mb-0" data-pricing-value="15">R$<span class="price">3</span><span class="h6 text-muted ml-2">/ por mês</span></h1>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body pt-0">
                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                        <li>Aluguel de 1 filme por semana.</li>
                        <li>Para quem gosta de cinema mas só consegue ver de fim de semana!</li>
                        <li>Sem taxa de cancelamento!</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="login" role="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary mb-3">Crie sua conta</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-pricing popular shadow text-center px-3 mb-4">
                <span class="h6 w-60 mx-auto px-4 py-1 rounded-bottom bg-primary text-white shadow-sm">Entusiasta</span>
                <div class="bg-transparent card-header pt-4 border-0">
                    <h1 class="h1 font-weight-normal text-primary text-center mb-0" data-pricing-value="30">R$<span class="price">6</span><span class="h6 text-muted ml-2">/ por mês</span></h1>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body pt-0">
                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                      <li>Aluguel de 3 filmes por semana!</li>
                      <li>Para você que ama cinema e não passa sem ver seus filmes favoritos!</li>
                      <li>Sem taxa de cancelamento!</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="login" role="button"class="btn btn-primary mb-3">Crie sua conta</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card card-pricing text-center px-3 mb-4">
                <span class="h6 w-60 mx-auto px-4 py-1 rounded-bottom bg-primary text-white shadow-sm">Cinéfilo</span>
                <div class="bg-transparent card-header pt-4 border-0">
                    <h1 class="h1 font-weight-normal text-primary text-center mb-0" data-pricing-value="45">R$<span class="price">9</span><span class="h6 text-muted ml-2">/ por mês</span></h1>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body pt-0">
                    <ul class="list-unstyled mb-4">
                      <li>Aluguel de 5 filmes por semana!!</li>
                      <li>Para os doentes por filmes!!</li>
                      <li>Sem taxa de cancelamento!</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="login" role="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary mb-3">Crie sua conta</a>
                </div>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
   
    
    <%- include('./partials/footer')%>

<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

